title: Dead To Rights_PC_English_by_A.Shioshvili
description:
Dead to Rights system requirements (minimum)

CPU: Pentium 4 or Athlon

CPU SPEED: 1.0 Ghz

RAM: 1 gb

OS: any windows xp x64 / any windows vista x64 / windows 7 sp1 x64 / windows 8.1 x64 / 
windows 10 x64 (8.1 and 10 may require install net framework 3.5 and 4.7.2)

VIDEO CARD: 16 MB DirectX 9.0 compatible Video Card with Hardware T&L

DIRECTX VERSION: 9.0 (included)

SOUND CARD: Yes


Dead to Rights Recommended Requirements

CPU: core 2 duo or Athlon

CPU SPEED: 2.4 Ghz

RAM: 2 gb or more

OS: any windows xp x64 / any windows vista x64 / windows 7 sp1 x64 / windows 8.1 x64 / 
windows 10 x64 (8.1 and 10 may require install net framework 3.5 and 4.7.2)

VIDEO CARD: 64 MB DirectX 9.0 compliant Video Card

DIRECTX VERSION: 9.0 (included)

SOUND CARD: Yes
